    "narrative_text": {
      "type": "_blocks",
      "blocks": {
        "paragraph_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Our beginning traces back to when our company founders, John and Jean Overdevest, left war-torn <em>Holland</em> and settled in southern New Jersey. The nursery started in <em>1952</em> with a focus on Azaleas, Rhododendrons, Dogwoods, and Japanese Maples. Through sheer <em>determination</em> and a pioneering spirit, they grew a backyard farm into a respected nursery. Their philosophy of <em>excellence</em> paired with <em>integrity</em> and <em>service</em> attracted independently-owned garden centers.</p>",
            "width": "100%",
            "max_width": "narrow",
            "type_preset": "rte",
            "alignment": "center",
            "padding-block-start": 0,
            "padding-block-end": 0
          }
        },
        "paragraph_2": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>As the <em>third-generation</em> of family enters the business, our commitment to <em>quality</em> and <em>sustainability</em> grows stronger each year. Our <em>passionate team</em> members carry the founding principles of hard work and hand-crafted excellence, working every day to bring you <em>happiness</em> with each planting.</p>",
            "width": "100%",
            "max_width": "narrow",
            "type_preset": "rte",
            "alignment": "center",
            "padding-block-start": 0,
            "padding-block-end": 0
          }
        },
        "paragraph_3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>While we have achieved awards throughout our history, the <em>best reward</em> continues to be the sincere compliments from our many <em>longstanding customers</em> who rely on us as their trusted source for the highest quality plants.</p>",
            "width": "100%",
            "max_width": "narrow",
            "type_preset": "rte",
            "alignment": "center",
            "padding-block-start": 0,
            "padding-block-end": 0
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": ["paragraph_1", "paragraph_2", "paragraph_3"],
      "settings": {
        "content_direction": "column",
        "horizontal_alignment_flex_direction_column": "center",
        "vertical_alignment_flex_direction_column": "center",
